chore(perf): rebaseline after Phase 3 supabase-js UMD landed

The previous baseline pre-dated supabase-js (Phase 3), so the
transferBytes gate was failing 35375 to 50400 by design. UX-felt
metrics (TBT 0, click-to-paint medians 21-26ms) are healthy under
Fast 3G; resetting transferBytes to the new equilibrium (50400 bytes)
so future regressions are caught against the post-Phase-3 floor.

10 runs per config.

